  "description": "<h3>📱 Phone Repair Sales Executive</h3><p><strong>Location:</strong> Chinatown / Tampines / Jurong / Yishun<br /><strong>Salary:</strong> $2800 basic + commission<br /><br /><strong>Apply via WhatsApp:</strong> 9456 6455</p><p><br /><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Handle walk-in & WhatsApp enquiries</p></li><li><p>Sell phone repair services (screen, battery, motherboard, etc.)</p></li><li><p>Explain repair options & pricing clearly to customers</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with technicians and follow up on repairs</p></li><li><p>Basic counter & customer service duties</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>At least 3 years experience in phone sales or phone repair sales</strong></p></li><li><p>Familiar with iPhone / Samsung / Android repairs</p></li><li><p>Good communication & closing skills</p></li><li><p>Independent, responsible, retail experience preferred</p></li></ul><p><strong>Why Join Us:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Expanding company with multiple outlets</p></li><li><p>Stable income + commission</p></li><li><p>Long-term growth opportunity</p></li></ul><p>📲 <strong>Apply via WhatsApp:</strong> 9456 6455</p>",
